*Sudija* je donela odluku. (The judge has made a decision.)
On je na suđenju zaštitio svoju čast i čast *sudije*. (He defended his honour and the judge's honour at the trial.)
Ona je uložila žalbu *sudiji*. (She filed an appeal to the judge.)
Mnogi smatraju da je *sudija* donela nepravednu odluku. (Many people think that the judge made an unfair decision.)
Niko nije očekivao da će *sudija* doneti ovu presudu. (No one expected the judge to make this verdict.)